    },
    {
      "start": 69.1,
      "end": 75.16,
      "text": "아, 각색도 하고, 각본도 하고, 결국엔 이렇게 영화감독으로 데뷔도"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.16,
      "end": 76.22,
      "text": "한 작품이라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.36,
      "end": 78.08,
      "text": "He's a man of multiple talents."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.32,
      "end": 81.12,
      "text": "He's actually, I said his name sounds German, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.56,
      "end": 83.72,
      "text": "But, surprise, surprise, he's French."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.98,
      "end": 84.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.46,
      "end": 86.64,
      "text": "Florian, my cousin's name is Florian."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.74,
      "end": 88.02,
      "text": "I know a few Florians."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.28,
      "end": 89.06,
      "text": "They're all German."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.22,
      "end": 90.46,
      "text": "But he is French."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.5,
      "end": 95.54,
      "text": "He's a French novelist, playwright, theater director, screenwriter, and film director."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.54,
      "end": 107.08,
      "text": "So, he wears many hats, and he's written over a dozen plays which have been staged worldwide and have made him one of the most celebrated contemporary playwrights to ever live."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.6,
      "end": 108.78,
      "text": "Contemporary playwrights."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.78,
      "end": 114.84,
      "text": "So, like, currently, you know, you know, modern, living, Shakespeare age 다르게."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.84,
      "end": 119.04,
      "text": "But, I think he has many hats."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.0,
      "end": 121.74,
      "text": "Did you like that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.78,
      "end": 122.48,
      "text": "Oh, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.54,
      "end": 123.14,
      "text": "Oh, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.2,
      "end": 127.34,
      "text": "I just came up with that one on the top of my head."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.34,
      "end": 128.54,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.76,
      "end": 131.02,
      "text": "즉각적으로 이렇게 떠올리신 표현이라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.46,
      "end": 134.64,
      "text": "이 versatile이라는 한 단어로도 저는 상상을 했었거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.82,
      "end": 135.3,
      "text": "Versatile."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.44,
      "end": 136.98,
      "text": "Oh, 그 말을 하려고 했는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.06,
      "end": 137.42,
      "text": "Ah."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.56,
      "end": 138.34,
      "text": "Has many hats."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.44,
      "end": 138.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.78,
      "end": 140.06,
      "text": "You have many hats."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.5,
      "end": 144.34,
      "text": "You are a DJ and a teacher and a singer and a singer and a..."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.34,
      "end": 144.82,
      "text": "뭐 있겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.72,
      "end": 147.78,
      "text": "좀 더 해봐요라고 하고 싶었는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.98,
      "end": 149.02,
      "text": "아, 그거 이어서 해야죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.12,
      "end": 150.54,
      "text": "We have to finish each other's sentences."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.8,
      "end": 152.9,
      "text": "You know, like Olaf and what's his name."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.24,
      "end": 154.66,
      "text": "Finish each other's sentences."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.66,
      "end": 156.9,
      "text": "Look, Anna랑 크리스토프죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.28,
      "end": 158.76,
      "text": "노래 100번 들여가지고."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.9,
      "end": 159.46,
      "text": "그랬구나."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.68,
      "end": 160.62,
      "text": "저는 잘 모르겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.76,
      "end": 162.58,
      "text": "We finish each other's sandwiches."
