    {
      "start": 231.23,
      "end": 232.11,
      "text": "The evening dose."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.83,
      "end": 233.87,
      "text": "Then you'll feel better."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.61,
      "end": 238.03,
      "text": "You know, it's been going on for some time."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.83,
      "end": 241.21,
      "text": "Strange things going on there under."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.33,
      "end": 243.01,
      "text": "Haven't you noticed?"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.62,
      "end": 244.86,
      "text": "Huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.6,
      "end": 249.42,
      "text": "It was this man claiming this was not my flat."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.75,
      "end": 253.25,
      "text": "Really unsympathetic looking man."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.31,
      "end": 254.77,
      "text": "A bit like your husband, only worse."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.63,
      "end": 256.75,
      "text": "It's the best yet, don't you think?"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.77,
      "end": 257.43,
      "text": "In my flat."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.43,
      "end": 262.27,
      "text": "Anthony가요, said it was his flat."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.47,
      "end": 263.55,
      "text": "It was his house."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.65,
      "end": 264.47,
      "text": "His apartment."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.81,
      "end": 271.01,
      "text": "어, 그런데 지금 Anne의 남편이라는 사람은 said no, 아니라고 한 상황이고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.19,
      "end": 275.53,
      "text": "그 다음에는 이 딸인 Anne이요, 얼굴이 바뀌었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.35,
      "end": 277.15,
      "text": "Facelift?"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.33,
      "end": 280.23,
      "text": "이번에는 얼굴이 바뀐 그런 장면이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.23,
      "end": 285.27,
      "text": "그래서 또 다른 얼굴을 한 사람인데 자신이 Anne이라고 하면서, 딸이라고 하면서,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.27,
      "end": 289.51,
      "text": "그래서 점점 더 혼란스러워지고 있는 상황이긴 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 289.73,
      "end": 290.91,
      "text": "So let me get this straight."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.99,
      "end": 292.87,
      "text": "Her face changed."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.31,
      "end": 297.51,
      "text": "It's actually a different actress or she's wearing some kind of mask or makeup."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.17,
      "end": 298.77,
      "text": "Different actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.23,
      "end": 300.11,
      "text": "This is crazy."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.25,
      "end": 301.45,
      "text": "I'm so confused."
    },
    {
      "start": 301.63,
      "end": 302.53,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.95,
      "end": 308.45,
      "text": "역지사지에 완벽하게 정확한, 적합한 그런 장면들이 연결이 되고 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 308.45,
      "end": 310.45,
      "text": "Yeah, I feel like I have dementia."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.63,
      "end": 311.97,
      "text": "We have dementia."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.49,
      "end": 315.07,
      "text": "자, 주요 표현들 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.95,
      "end": 318.55,
      "text": "Strange things going on around us."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.65,
      "end": 321.05,
      "text": "응, 딱 제 말이 바로 이 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.55,
      "end": 323.61,
      "text": "Strange things going on around us."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.67,
